comment_data.body:
It seems that extension was renamed to sphinx.ext.imgmath in the 1.8 release of sphinx sphinx-doc/sphinx#6182. So if you want to build the 0.29.x documentation you will either have to use a version of sphinx that supports it or rename the extension in the source. That change should probably be backported to for the next 0.29 release together with an appropriate `doc-requirements.txt`. 

Version for 0.29.22: https://github.com/cython/cython/blob/4562fb26d2cfabf2361f45bcd5268b6bebf6d5ae/docs/conf.py#L41-L47

and master: https://github.com/cython/cython/blob/b3f8a198d96727c9111dbc707a05e286b93c974c/docs/conf.py#L36-L42

OK so after correctiong list of sphoinx extensions to the same as master I'm able to generate man page.
